<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>STP Team</title>

<style>
    body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background: #0e1217;
        color: #e5e7eb;
        margin: 0;
    }

    .container {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 60px auto;
        background: #161b22;
        padding: 40px;
        border-radius: 14px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(40,199,111,0.2);
        animation: fade 1s ease;
    }

    h1 { color: #28c76f; }
    h2 { color: #1cd673; }

    .member {
        background: #1c222b;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        border-left: 4px solid #28c76f;
    }

    @keyframes fade {
        from { opacity:0; transform:translateY(20px); }
        to { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); }
    }
</style>
</head>

<body>
<div class="container">

<h1>STP Core Team</h1>

<div class="member">
    <h2>Founder</h2>
    <p>Responsible for vision, global strategy, partnerships, and ecosystem direction.</p>
</div>

<div class="member">
    <h2>Blockchain Developer</h2>
    <p>Creates smart contracts, tokenomics architecture, and backend infrastructure.</p>
</div>

<div class="member">
    <h2>Marketing Lead</h2>
    <p>Community management, brand development, international outreach.</p>
</div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
